## Constraints

- Manager hierarchy cycle detection — recursive SQL veya iterative check
- Soft delete only — `is_active = false`, hard delete yasak
- Anonymization hard — PII fields → hash, anonymized_at set
- Self-protection — user kendi hesabını deactivate edemez
- Master data ownership — her user company'ye bağlı
- Master data cannot be deleted if referenced (soft delete or archive)

## Done Definition

- [ ] Users CRUD: create, list, detail, update, deactivate, reactivate, anonymize
- [ ] Sessions: list, revoke individual, revoke all
