- [ ] Permission: USER_CREATE, USER_LIST_VIEW, USER_UPDATE_ATTRIBUTE, USER_DEACTIVATE, USER_SESSION_VIEW, USER_SESSION_REVOKE, USER_ANONYMIZE, MASTER_DATA_VIEW, MASTER_DATA_MANAGE — tümü seed'de + metadata
- [ ] Integration tests full CRUD flow per module
- [ ] `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm test`, `pnpm test:integration` — green

